CompartidaHakariKarane: {
	Mision1: {
		Titulo: You must choose only one, or maybe not?
		Descripcion: Get a special gift for both girls; using a scythe on the grass might help.
		Bloqueado: You must choose only one, or maybe not?: Requires: Complete Karane's "The Tsundere's Forgiveness." Hakari and Karane must be following the player. Progress is shared by both.
		Dialogo0: Well {0}... Who will you fall madly in love with?
		Dialogo1: Huh? You...
		Dialogo2: can find out after this short break!
		Dialogo3: I'm gonna kick your ass!
		Dialogo4: *Thought: I... I can't possibly choose!*
		Completacion0: So, what's your answer? We are dying to know!
		Completacion1: Yeah.
		Completacion2: I want both of you to be my girlfriends!
		Completacion3: HUUUUUUUUUUUUuuuuuuuuh??!!
		Completacion4: You wanna date us both?? Did you wake up on the stupid side of the bed?!
		Completacion5: Maybe I did.
		Completacion6: And maybe my idea's not the typical solution, but...
		Completacion7: I know better than anyone. It takes a hell of a lot of courage to confess to that special someone you love!
		Completacion8: I thought about it all night and couldn't decide! Because I'm falling in love with both of you!
		Completacion9: There's no way I can pick just one! I may be two-timing, but I'll never hurt you! I vow to give it my all!
		Completacion10: I'm going to make you the happiest girls alive! So, I'm begging you! Please say you'll be my girlfriends!
		Completacion11: ...
		Completacion12: Huh?
		Completacion13: You can sweet-talk me all you want, but two-timing's not on the table—
		Completacion14: esta linea no sirve de nada xd
		Completacion15: Huh?
		Completacion16: Huh?
		Completacion17: Pink four-leaf clovers! We looked for those for hours! We could not manage to find even one, and somehow you have two!
		Completacion18: Jeez! You're seriously dense! You should have left that dumb, baby superstition crap back in middle school, you loser!
		Completacion19: Inda, please calm down. Your words are coming back to bite both you and me.
		Completacion20: Hah! I bet you're trying to show off how much you care for us!
		Completacion21: I'm still not letting you talk me into accepting something as trashy as two-timing!
		Completacion22: Huh! Oh, sorry. That's not what I was going for at all.
		Completacion23: THEN WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU TRYING TO DO??!!
		Completacion24: I figured if I gave you these clovers along with my answer, then maybe I might get to see those beautiful smiles.
		Completacion25: WUAAAAAAAAAAA!!
		Completacion26: I-I appreciate it and I accept.
		Completacion27: HUhhh??!! Don't tell me that you caught the dumb disease, too!
		Completacion28: My feelings are real. I'm hopelessly in love with you.
		Completacion29: I cannot imagine falling for someone else. You are all I will ever want!
		Completacion30: WUUUAAAIIIAAAAAA!!!
		Completacion31: Hey, that all goes for me, too! If you don't treat me right, I cross my heart I'll make you pay!
		Completacion32: Yeah, I promise. You're gonna be the happiest girls in the world!
	}

	Mision2: {
		Titulo: A three-way kiss
		Descripcion: Have an incredible adventure with your first girlfriends!
		Bloqueado: A three-way kiss: Requires: Complete "You must choose only one, or maybe not?". Hakari and Karane must be following the player. Progress is shared by both.
		Dialogo0: Uh, weird but... speaking of kissing, you have had your first kiss, have you not?
		Dialogo1: Huh? Not yet. You two are my first-ever girlfriends, y'know.
		Dialogo2: *Thoughts: That means whoever acts first won't only be the first to kiss him, but his first kiss of all time!*
		Dialogo3: You know I can see your dialogue windows and read what you're thinking, right?
		Dialogo4: The script is already written; there will be a kiss, but first we must complete a special mission!
		Dialogo5: And what special mission would we have to overcome, {0}?
		Dialogo6: You'll have to join me on an adventure and kill 50 creatures!
		Dialogo7: WHO WAS IN CHARGE OF DESIGNING THIS TRASH MISSION?!
		Dialogo8: I have no idea! But that's how the dev wants it!
		Dialogo9: There's no time to lose, girls! LET'S GO!
		Completacion0: We finally completed the objective!
		Completacion1: Karane, what's next in the script? Is our little kiss coming up? Mehehe.
		Completacion2: *Reading the script*
		Completacion3: We do it at the same time?!
		Completacion4: Yep, a three-way kiss.
		Completacion5: It wouldn't only be a special moment with me. You would also be kissing each other.
		Completacion6: WUUUUUUUAAAA!!!!
		Completacion7: At first, I figured you wouldn't be up for it if you were on bad terms.
		Completacion8: But it'll be okay. I believe in you. Actually, I should say I believe in us!
		Completacion9: Okay, don't get too hyped up here now, you weirdo...
		Completacion10: Hurry up, hit the complete button and KISS US FAST!!
	}
}

Shizuka: {
	Mision1: {
		Titulo: The Silent Princess and the Terrarian
		Descripcion: It seems she has a hard time talking to others, find a way to help her communicate.
		Bloqueado: The Silent Princess and the Terrarian: Requires: Completing "A Kiss of Three".
		Dialogo0: ...
		Dialogo1: ":)"
		Dialogo2: (⸝⸝O-O⸝⸝)
		Dialogo3: (⸝⸝>-<⸝⸝)
		Dialogo4: Such incredible dialogue was implemented for this character...
		Dialogo5: Why don't you just speak clearly to me?
		Dialogo6: (｡Ó-Ò｡)
		Dialogo7: (◞‸ ◟)
		Dialogo8: I see...
		Completacion0: Here, this is for you. It's a phone with a text-to-speech app that will read out whatever you type.
		Completacion1: If speaking out loud can be scary for me sometimes, I can't begin to imagine how hard it must be for you.
		Completacion2: I'd never want to make you talk if you don't want to, but I wanted to help you.
		Completacion3: So, you can have an easier way to communicate with others. I really hope that this phone can do you some good.
		Completacion4: Now, why don't we give this thing a shot? Is there anything that you would like to say to me?
		Completacion5: ...
		Completacion6: *Cellphone: I love you.*
		Completacion7: ...
		Completacion8: *Cellphone: I apologize. Pray, pay it no heed.*
		Completacion9: *Cellphone: I ask not for an answer.*
		Completacion10: *Cellphone: I know there is already a maiden promised to you.*
		Completacion11: *Cellphone: I only wish to make my feelings known.*
		Completacion12: Praise be, for I am in love with you, too!
		Completacion13: *Cellphone: Though our love be strong, our paths are destined never to converge.*
		Completacion14: If fate's walls separate us.
		Completacion15: We need only to break them down!
		Completacion16: Let's go forth together, Shizuka!
	}

	Mision2: {
		Titulo: One more? Who cares?
		Descripcion: Introduce Shizuka to your girlfriends.
		Bloqueado: One more? Who cares?: Requires: Hakari and Karane must be following the player.
		Dialogo0: I guess I have to introduce my new girlfriend to my other girlfriends...
		Dialogo1: Oh, I'm so scared!
		Completacion0: Hi girls... I wanted to ask you a question.
		Completacion1: What's wrong, {0}?
		Completacion2: I just completed Shizuka Yoshimoto's mission 1 and...
		Completacion3: Could I please have your permission to make Shizuka my newest girlfriend?
		Completacion4: DID YOU ALREADY DUMB BRAIN ROT AWAY? IT'S EITHER THAT OR YOU WANNA DIEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!
		Completacion5: My darling, it can't be...
		Completacion6: You have found a new love, yet in your endless kindness, you have the immense grace not to put us out in a cardboard box on the sidewalk!
		Completacion7: It's a freakin' brain rot epidemic up in here!
		Completacion8: No! My feelings for you two haven't shifted away toward Shizuka!
		Completacion9: Let me explain. You won't be sharing the spoils from the same old oil field. I'm gonna cherish you two plus Shizuka as much as I always have. It'll be just the same.
		Completacion10: NO! IT'LL BE EVEN MORE LOVE AND TEN TIMES BETTER!
		Completacion11: Do you think you're capable of that?
		Completacion12: Yeah, and if I'm ever not living up to my vow, I need you to tell me at once.
		Completacion13: I swear to atone for it by... Drinking red potion.
		Completacion14: How do you even plan to get one in a vanilla world?!
		Completacion15: Oh, how manly! Sweep me up into your warrior's arms, my love!
		Completacion16: Alright. These ladies are my girlfriends Hakari Hanazono and Karane Inda.
		Completacion17: It is an honor to meet you.
		Completacion18: Yeah. What's up dude?
		Completacion19: As for the two of you meet my new girlfriend. Shizuka Yoshimoto.
		Completacion20: How is she programmed?
		Completacion21: According to her code, she has no built-in dialogue.
		Completacion22: *Cellphone: Oh, happy day. 'Tis a pleasure to make thine acquaintance.
		Completacion23: SHE IS LIKE AN AI!
	}

	Mision3: {
		Titulo: No Holding Back
		Descripcion: Have an amazing adventure with Shizuka alone! Eliminate enemies in the cursed biome. For the counter to progress, Hakari and Karane must no longer be following you.
		Bloqueado: No Holding Back: Requires: Hakari, Karane and Shizuka are following the player.
		Dialogo0: Girls, sorry. I gotta step away for a sec, I'll be AFK for a bit.
		Dialogo1: ...
		Dialogo2: We gotta talk, Yoshimoto. What the heck is your deal?
		Dialogo3: ...
		Dialogo4: Be real! You would've gotten all up in there if we weren't here! Why are you acting so freakin' dumb?
		Dialogo5: I doubt she can hear her own thoughts over your yelling. If she had gone all in, you would've yelled at her then, too.
		Dialogo6: Fat chance! I've never yelled at anybody in my entire life, stupid!
		Dialogo7: *Cellphone: The two of you were spoken for by... {0}. Long before I was. As a newcomer, I must stay out of your way.*
		Dialogo8: I had a feeling you'd say something like that. Well, wake up! You're just as much his girlfriend as the two of us, Lady Bookworm!
		Dialogo9: So stop hesitating and do what you wanna do! I've got no patience for this crap! It makes me sick watching you fumble around instead of just admitting how you feel!
		Dialogo10: Says the girlfriend who would much rather pick a fight than admit how she feels at any given moment.
		Dialogo11: SHUT YOUR MOUTH OR I'LL SHUT IT FOR YOU!! ARE YOU TRYING TO PICK A FIGHT OR WHAT??!!
		Dialogo12: *Cellphone: I apologize. You are correct.*
		Dialogo13: That's exactly what I'm talking about! Don't let me walk all over you. Fight back!
		Dialogo14: If that is the case, I will speak from the heart. In truth, I am quite petrified with fear.
		Dialogo15: Well that hurts... do you guys really think I'm so scary? T_T
		Dialogo16: Interesting that you care after all.
		Dialogo17: *Cellphone: Forgive me. I have misspoken. What I fear is...*
		Dialogo18: *Cellphone: Hanazono... she carries herself with elegance and grace. She is the very picture of a lady, and her charm is undeniable.*
		Dialogo19: *Cellphone: Inda... she is a beauty blessed with the face of an angel, and she carries herself with the confidence of a queen.*
		Dialogo20: *Cellphone: If I were to stand beside you as an equal, {0} will surely compare us. I fear that most of all.*
		Dialogo21: What the heck?
		Dialogo22: Oh my goodness.
		Dialogo23: That's the most adorable thing I've ever heard in my life!
		Dialogo24: *Cellphone: I am ordinary. Plain as they come. My form is more that of a child than a woman. My personality... quiet and gloomy.*
		Dialogo25: *Cellphone: In your company, the difference is night and day.*
		Dialogo26: Hey. Stop, don't be like that. I think you're plenty cute yourself. You're dainty and gentle. Those are awesome qualities for a girl to have.
		Dialogo27: I'm sorry for getting all pissed off at you.
		Dialogo28: As she should be! You have nothing to worry about. She has been pissed off as long as I have known her!
		Dialogo29: Hey.
		Dialogo30: Also, I don't know how he does it, but {0}'s love runs deeper than we could ever possibly imagine. I'm sure he could list dozens of things he likes about you.
		Dialogo31: Like I was saying, you've gotta stop holding back with him just 'cause you're scared of us! If you've ever got something to say or do, you have our blessing to go for it! Ya got that?
		Dialogo32: Amazing. That went better than I ever expected.
		Dialogo33: Since Karane seemed furious at Shizuka, I pretended to go AFK. If I want the girls to get along, I can't be getting in the way.
		Dialogo34: Just like I thought, Karane wasn't mad, just frustrated.
		Dialogo35: But I'm glad Hakari's there to deflect some of that rage.
		Dialogo36: It looks like Shizuka's gonna take Karane's advice and let her wants and wishes flow free!
		Dialogo37: MY HEARTTTT!
		Dialogo38: Did you miss me??!!
		Dialogo39: Hey {0}, we decided Shizuka's going on an adventure with you. Just the two of you!
		Dialogo40: That's right! You wanna go on an adventure with {0}, don't you Shizuka?
		Dialogo41: *Cellphone: I want to do it.*
		Completacion0: *Cellphone: This adventure was... so much fun. The kind of experience worthy of an OVA.*
		Completacion1: Yes! It was incredible, Shizuka. We can go on as many adventures as you want, whenever you want.
		Completacion2: *Cellphone: I will be by your side at all times, wherever you go...*
		Completacion3: Thank you, Shizuka. That really means a lot to me... I love you.
		Completacion4: *Cellphone: I love you too, my lord...*
		Completacion5: ...
		Completacion6: Oh? What's up, Shizuka?
		Completacion7: *Cellphone: I wish to be kissed.*
		Completacion8: Huh!?
		Completacion9: *Cellphone: Deep in her heart bubbled the urge to lay her lips upon his.*
		Completacion10: I'm truly honored. Jeez, I can't wait!
	}

