Nano: {
	Mision1: {
		Titulo: The Hyper-Efficient Girl
		Descripcion: It seems Nano Eiai has something to tell you.
		Bloqueado: The Hyper-Efficient Girl: Requires completing Shizuka's "No Holding Back".
		Dialogo0: Looks like you're new around here. I've been watching you. Your name is Nano Eiai, right?
		Dialogo1: Correct. You must be {0}. I've already heard about you.
		Dialogo2: Why do I feel like some massive force is crushing me?
		Completacion0: "{0}. Ever since I appeared in this world, I've concluded that I love you."
		Completacion1: With that said, let's enter a relationship.
		Completacion2: That's perfect. 'Cause I'm in love with you too, Eiai. I would be honored to go out with you.
		Completacion3: I must decline.
		Completacion4: WHAT IN THE PUNKED IS THIS CRAP??!!
		Completacion5: The ideal outcome would've been for you to deny my request and leave me in peace, but no, you've ruined my plan and left me with no choice. I had to do it myself.
		Completacion6: The reason I came here is to put an end to this love.
		Completacion7: Matrimony and then childbirth. That's what romance brings. And at this moment, I'm in no need of either.
		Completacion8: Romance is meaningless. A complete waste of time.
		Completacion9: So let me be clear, I am never going to go out with you.
		Completacion10: ...
		Completacion11: Goodbye.
		Completacion12: Bad news! I'm sorry to break it to you. But unlike you, my heart is stronger. It takes more than a breakup to end this love!
		Completacion13: Fine, but that's irrelevant to me.
		Completacion14: If I refuse to fall out of love, your rejection isn't exactly ending this romance once and for all, is it?
		Completacion15: "{0} is in love with me! 3.141592653589793..."
		Completacion16: You're tough. But I'm not gonna give up. I can't just draw a line in the sand like you.
		Completacion17: Humor me. Let's go out on a date. One day's all I'm asking for!
		Completacion18: That would be...
		Completacion19: If I really can't win you over, I promise I'll be out of your hair for good!
	}

	Mision2: {
		Titulo: A Thermal Stroll
		Descripcion: Have a great time on your date with Nano; use a camera to capture photos with Nano in hell and the snow.
		Bloqueado: A Thermal Stroll: Requires: Nano must be following the player, no other girlfriend must be following you.
		Dialogo0: Where will our date be, {0}?
		Dialogo1: I have planned several quite exceptional locations.
		Dialogo2: I have a clear mission today, show Eiai the time of her life!
		Dialogo3: I need her to realize how important fun can be. And that love is the most meaningful thing on this planet!
		Completacion0: So Eiai, we're halfway through our date. How have you been enjoying it so far?
		Completacion1: I have not obtained anything of value so far.
		Completacion2: Snow is simply water in a crystallized solid state.
		Completacion3: On the other hand, going to hell is a decision devoid of logic. The heat is so extreme that appreciating the scenery is simply impossible.
		Completacion4: That's part of the world's charm, we're defying logic together!
		Completacion5: You didn't tell me you had an instant camera.
		Completacion6: You know about these? I've always had a thing for them for some reason. You, too?
		Completacion7: They retain neither film negatives nor digital data. Therefore if the photograph is lost, so too is all record of the event. Quite illogical.
		Completacion8: A one-star review.
		Completacion9: Well, moving right along from that hiccup.
		Completacion10: Look at these, you look super pretty here. Check it.
		Completacion11: How very illogical.
	}

	Mision3: {
		Titulo: NanUp: A High-Rise Adventure
		Descripcion: Get one last memory on a floating island. You must talk to Nano on the floating island to continue.
		Bloqueado: NanUp: A High-Rise Adventure: Requires: Nano must be following the player, no other girlfriend must be following you.
		Dialogo0: What are we doing now?
		Dialogo1: We're heading to one last place. Since this is a date, a special spot like this couldn't be left out.
		Dialogo2: This is all I've got left. I really hope Nano enjoys this, it's my last shot!
		Completacion0: We finally made it! Too bad there's a height limit, the views up here are incredible.
		Completacion1: ...
		Completacion2: Yes... The scenery can be appreciated very efficiently from up here...
		Completacion3: ...
		Completacion4: Wait a second, your hand is shaking. Does that mean you're afraid of heights?
		Completacion5: Please, it's only natural to fear life-threatening elevations. It's a mere survival instinct I can't overwrite. Gosh, my bad.
		Completacion6: Don't worry, Eiai, it's time we headed back. I'll stay right by your side until we're back on the ground.
	}

	Mision4: {
		Titulo: Something Worth It
		Descripcion: Nano Eiai has a few last things to tell you.
		Bloqueado: Something Worth It: Requires: Have all 3 photos (Underworld, snow and sky). Get off the floating island if you're still on it.
		Dialogo0: We're back down, Eiai. Solid ground at last.
		Dialogo1: After being up there, the ground feels a whole lot safer.
		Dialogo2: That was one crazy ride, wasn't it? From extreme cold to that unbearable heat...
		Dialogo3: Yes, though I am not used to experiencing so many different things in such a short amount of time.
		Completacion0: What'd you think of the day overall?
		Completacion1: It's true that I enjoyed myself. Far more than expected.
		Completacion2: Really? Does that mean...
		Completacion3: However, enjoyment was all it was. A great example of useless fun.
		Completacion4: I'm no closer to success than before. It was just a meaningless day.
		Completacion5: I'm sorry...
		Completacion6: C'mon, no need to apologize for that. We're all entitled to our opinions.
		Completacion7: I'm happy you told me. A lot of folks would've found it easier to smile and lie.
		Completacion8: Well, it's a shame. But since it was a meaningless day, there's no point in looking back on it down the road.
		Completacion9: Let's erase the whole thing... I'll toss the photos in the trash slot.
		Completacion10: ...
		Completacion11: Ah! Wait!
		Completacion12: Thought so. We both understand you can't lose something that you don't have. But just a second ago, you were certainly afraid of losing something.
		Completacion13: Then today, you gained something you didn't have before going on this date with me! Any gain is value, isn't it?
		Completacion14: Don't you see where I'm coming from? We made something new! Sure, it might not be able to be defined in words or given a numerical score.
		Completacion15: And yeah, it probably won't be anything for your future. But it's something of so much value that you're already scared of losing it.
		Completacion16: That thing is yours!
		Completacion17: ...
		Completacion18: What is this...? Why am I... Crying...
		Completacion19: Sorry, I know that might've been hard, but I think you learned something important. Carving out special times to have fun is a really big deal.
		Completacion20: And at the end of the day, enjoying those moments and the people we share them with is what makes our lives meaningful.
		Completacion21: Feeling any better?
		Completacion22: Yes... Please, {0}. Enter into a relationship with me. I love you. I hope you feel the same way.
		Completacion23: I want to learn through this romance, to see all that I've been missing out on.
		Completacion24: All those meaningful times, I think I'm ready for them. If I can share them with you, that is.
		Completacion25: Eiai, I love you and feel the same way! Let's do this. Let's go out for real!
		Completacion26: ...
		Completacion27: I believe in fulfilling my desires without fretting over the means. It's efficient. Did you mind?
		Completacion28: No... Frankly, the opposite.
		Completacion29: I'll be keeping the photos.
	}

	Mision5: {
		Titulo: How Many Are Left?
		Descripcion: Introduce Nano to your girlfriends.
		Bloqueado: How Many Are Left?: Requires: All other girlfriends must be following you.
		Dialogo0: Well, here we go again...
		Dialogo1: Though I'm not nearly as nervous as the first time.
		Dialogo2: Hey girls!
		Completacion0: I went on a date with Nano... So, could I pretty please have you wonderful ladies' permission to make Nano Eiai my newest girlfriend?
